g-top: 3px; padding-bottom: 3px\" class=\"hierarchy\"><a href=\"https://build.fhir.org/ig/FHIR/ig-guidance/readingIgs.html#table-views\" title=\"Additional information about the element\">Description &amp; Constraints</a><span style=\"float: right\"><a href=\"https://build.fhir.org/ig/FHIR/ig-guidance/readingIgs.html#table-views\" title=\"Legend for this format\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"doco\" style=\"background-color: inherit\"/></a></span></th></tr><tr style=\"border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px; vertical-align: top; background-color: white\"><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px; white-space: nowrap; background-image: url(tbl_bck1.png)\" class=\"hierarchy\"><img src=\"tbl_spacer.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: inherit\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><img src=\"icon_element.gif\" alt=\".\" style=\"background-color: white; background-color: inherit\" title=\"Element\" class=\"hierarchy\"/> <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualProduct-definitions.html#PreQualProduct\" title=\"Logical model for WHO PreQual Product from the backend API#xA;with additional data fields for referencing associated FHIR and logical model data objects.\">PreQualProduct</a><a name=\"PreQualProduct\"> </a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"/><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">0</span><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">..</span><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">*</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\"><a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\">PreQualDBAPI</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px\" class=\"hierarchy\">WHO PreQual Product<br/><br/>Elements defined in Ancestors:<a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Vaccine Product ID (authoritative)\">productId</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Product reference name (e.g. FVP-P-447)\">productName</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Product type code from PreQualDatabaseMetadata (e.g. FinishedVaccineProduct)\">productType</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Date of prequalification acceptance\">dateOfPrequal</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Assessment procedure code from PreQualDatabaseMetadata (e.g. PrequalificationStandard)\">assessmentProcedure</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Product status code from PreQualDatabaseMetadata (e.g. Prequalified)\">status</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Pharmaceutical form code from PreQualDatabaseMetadata\">pharmaceuticalForm</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Presentation (e.g. Vial, Ampoule)\">presentation</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Number of doses per primary container\">numDoses</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Vaccine full name\">vaccineFullName</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Vaccine abbreviated name\">vaccineAbbreviatedName</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Vaccine commercial name\">vaccineCommercialName</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Vaccine type ID\">vaccineTypeId</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Route of administration code from PreQualDatabaseMetadata\">routeOfAdministration</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Applicant/manufacturer organization ID (may be absent if not yet assigned)\">applicantId</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Applicant/manufacturer organization name (always present from API data)\">applicantName</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Applicant organization address\">applicantAddress</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"NRA organization ID (may be absent if not yet assigned)\">nraId</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Responsible NRA name (always present from API data)\">nraName</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"NRA country\">nraCountry</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Shelf life (e.g. 24 months)\">shelfLife</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Storage temperature (e.g. 2 - 8°C)\">storageTemperature</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Diluent information\">diluent</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Last publishing date\">lastPublishingDate</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Publishing remarks\">publishingRemarks</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Preservative name (e.g. Thiomersal)\">preservative</a>, <a href=\"StructureDefinition-PreQualDBAPI.html\" title=\"Preservative concentration (e.g. 0.01%)\">preservativeConcentration</a><br/><span style=\"font-weight:bold\">Instances of this logical model can be the target of a Reference</span></td></tr>#xD;\n<tr style=\"border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px; vertical-align: top; background-color: #F7F7F7\"><td style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: #F7F7F7; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px; white-space: nowrap; background-image: url(tbl_bck10.png)\" class=\"hierarchy\"><img src=\"tbl_spacer.png\" alt=\".\" style=\"background